Shall be called with CachableBlockFile.Reader, TabletServerResourceManager.AssignmentWatcher, ClientContext, CachableBlockFile.Writer, MasterMetricsFactory, UserImpersonation, MetricsFactory, BloomFilterLayer.Reader, BCFile.Reader, BCFile.Writer, TabletServerMetricsFactory, Compactor, MapFileIterator, ZooConfiguration, InMemoryMap, TimedProcessor, CompactionWatcher, SessionManager, ReplicationProcessor, TabletIteratorEnvironment, TabletData, VolumeManagerImpl, TCredentialsUpdatingInvocationHandler, SaslServerConnectionParams, NamespaceConfiguration, KerberosAuthenticator, LogSorter, MajorCompactionRequest, SequentialWorkAssigner, DistributedWorkQueue, SaslConnectionParams, UnorderedWorkAssigner.

      • getProperties

        public abstract void getProperties(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> props,
                                   <any> filter)
        Returns property key/value pairs in this configuration. The pairs include those defined in this configuration which pass the given filter, and those supplied from the parent configuration which are not included from here.
        Parameters:
        props - properties object to populate
        filter - filter for accepting properties from this configuration

        public long getUpdateCount()
